, \"to\": 308}, {\"ngram\": \"her favourite discipline\", \"from\": 310, \"to\": 334}, {\"ngram\": \"the aching nerves\", \"from\": 350, \"to\": 367}, {\"ngram\": \"the pit\", \"from\": 381, \"to\": 388}, {\"ngram\": \"her stomach\", \"from\": 392, \"to\": 403}, {\"ngram\": \"the start line\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 421}, {\"ngram\": \"the sprints\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 437}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the former, she already has Olympic gold; in the latter, she is the favourite on the final day of the Games.\", \"from\": 440, \"to\": 551, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic gold\", \"from\": 471, \"to\": 483}, {\"ngram\": \"the final day\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 537}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 541, \"to\": 550}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The big question mark remains in the keirin itself, a race as much about tactical acumen and experience as the pure power and speed that are a prerequisite.\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 708, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 589, \"end\": 595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7699458211811624e-62, \"text\": \"keirin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The big question mark\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 573}, {\"ngram\": \"a race\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 610}, {\"ngram\": \"tactical acumen\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 640}, {\"ngram\": \"experience\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 655}, {\"ngram\": \"the pure power\", \"from\": 659, \"to\": 673}, {\"ngram\": \"speed\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 683}, {\"ngram\": \"a prerequisite\", \"from\": 693, \"to\": 707}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At just 21, she has not yet had time to master the wily arts of an event that was set up in Japan in the wake of the Second World War to boost its economy.\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 865, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 802, \"end\": 807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Empire_of_Japan\", \"